explanations.reason: The paper focuses on the impact of social distancing and social contact on the health outcomes of older adults during the COVID-19 pandemic. It uses cross-sectional and longitudinal analyses, logistic regression, and questionnaires to explore these relationships. There is no mention of any machine learning techniques, algorithms, or models in the title or abstract. The study is purely based on statistical analysis and survey data, not involving any of the listed machine learning or deep learning keywords.
